	&#8220;Oh my husband, why do you keep leaving me like this.  First in velious, against that Statue of Ralos Zek.  Then back there with Venril, and now&#8230;&#8221;  Ulla wept for herself, but more for her fallen husband.  &#8220;The gods have something planned for you Rillen, I just hope it doesn&#8217;t kill you.  I need you, you are my other half.  I love you with all my heart.<BR>
